def get_func(pyc_data):
    import imp
    import os
    import tempfile
    with tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(mode='w+b', suffix='.pyc', delete=False) as f:
        f.write(pyc_data)
        f.flush()
        pyc_file_path = f.name

        module_name = os.path.basename(pyc_file_path).replace('.pyc', '')
        spec = imp.find_module(module_name, [os.path.dirname(pyc_file_path)])
        my_module = imp.load_module(module_name, *spec)
        os.unlink(pyc_file_path)
        return my_module
